236
00:10:48,539 --> 00:10:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] Neke aplikacije ne može same skidati.

237
00:10:50,539 --> 00:10:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, roditelji, učite se.

238
00:10:51,539 --> 00:10:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, i evo sad ono,

239
00:10:52,539 --> 00:10:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga si upali, jel takviću.

240
00:10:54,539 --> 00:10:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može gledat,

241
00:10:55,539 --> 00:10:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] ne može ni skinut ništa novo bez našeg odobrenja,

242
00:10:57,539 --> 00:11:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] tako da tu se mi trudimo nekako bar malo filtrirati, jel?

243
00:11:00,539 --> 00:11:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] A gled, to je ta generacija.

244
00:11:02,539 --> 00:11:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] To mi na mene povjeljamo.

245
00:11:03,539 --> 00:11:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo, ono, odrasli.

246
00:11:04,539 --> 00:11:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Gold dvojka,

247
00:11:05,539 --> 00:11:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] gazeta unutra,

248
00:11:06,539 --> 00:11:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] bijeli maldvoro,

249
00:11:07,539 --> 00:11:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] i to je to, i laganica.

250
00:11:09,539 --> 00:11:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bilo ono najljepiš.

251
00:11:10,539 --> 00:11:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovo je lijepi primjer, to je roditelj.

252
00:11:12,539 --> 00:11:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, a mi se borimo koliko možemo, daj.

253
00:11:14,539 --> 00:11:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ne možeš.

254
00:11:15,539 --> 00:11:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] I znaš kaj, treba se baviti s njima, to je ono.

255
00:11:17,539 --> 00:11:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je nao žena priča.

256
00:11:18,539 --> 00:11:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kak se ne bavi s njima,

257
00:11:19,539 --> 00:11:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] baš je rekla,

258
00:11:20,539 --> 00:11:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] neka psihologica redavno pričala,

259
00:11:22,539 --> 00:11:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] veli da,

260
00:11:23,539 --> 00:11:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] kao si sjećate one zle mačehe,

261
00:11:25,539 --> 00:11:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] kak su slali djecu zle mačehe,

262
00:11:27,539 --> 00:11:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] to ti je danas, veli djeci,

263
00:11:29,539 --> 00:11:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] tutneš mobil u ruke dva, tri sata,

264
00:11:31,539 --> 00:11:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa šaljaš ih u to je digitalni svijet.

265
00:11:33,539 --> 00:11:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] I onda i ja sam isto na mobilu,

266
00:11:35,539 --> 00:11:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] na sebi isto ja sam ovisnik,

267
00:11:36,539 --> 00:11:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] misli je katastrofa.

268
00:11:37,539 --> 00:11:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sad dnevno, ono, malo radiš na društvene mreže,

269
00:11:39,539 --> 00:11:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa zalutam,

270
00:11:40,539 --> 00:11:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] i stavno baš se trudim,

271
00:11:41,539 --> 00:11:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] aj sad imam na moru,

272
00:11:42,539 --> 00:11:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja ti na moru,

273
00:11:43,539 --> 00:11:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] baš se na moru odmorim od tih, ono, matrem mobilitela.

274
00:11:46,539 --> 00:11:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] I mogu se pohvaliti,

275
00:11:47,539 --> 00:11:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] vrlo je korekta na svaku poruku čovjek

276
00:11:49,539 --> 00:11:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] odgovori svakati čast.

277
00:11:50,539 --> 00:11:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nema da fali.

278
00:11:51,539 --> 00:11:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko je došli učeru?

279
00:11:52,539 --> 00:11:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pol dvani si došli.

280
00:11:53,539 --> 00:11:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao da, pozvao sam da se vidimo.

281
00:11:55,539 --> 00:11:56,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, tamo smo s tekme došli.

282
00:11:56,539 --> 00:11:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] A dobro, ali ne, serijice, bez vrke.

283
00:11:59,539 --> 00:12:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] Svaka čast na ovo zaraditelstvo,

284
00:12:01,539 --> 00:12:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] treba te malo mlade...

285
00:12:02,539 --> 00:12:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] Treba, treba, biće borba.

286
00:12:04,539 --> 00:12:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam malo ono,

287
00:12:05,539 --> 00:12:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] frapiran s nekih stvarima koje može.

288
00:12:07,539 --> 00:12:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko bi recimo ti,

289
00:12:08,539 --> 00:12:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] da li uopće koristiš u poslu svom?

290
00:12:10,539 --> 00:12:11,539
[SPEAKER_01] Umjetnu inteligenciju.

291
00:12:11,539 --> 00:12:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] Umjetnu inteligenciju.

292
00:12:12,539 --> 00:12:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo sad sam koristio za nekakve...

293
00:12:14,539 --> 00:12:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mi si nemino na to pitati?

294
00:12:15,539 --> 00:12:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, znaš za kaj koristim.

295
00:12:17,539 --> 00:12:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dobio sam jedna peća skill-a,

296
00:12:18,539 --> 00:12:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] sada koje bih htio skinuti.

297
00:12:20,539 --> 00:12:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] I učer sam baš upisao,

298
00:12:22,539 --> 00:12:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] na večer daj mi najbolje razloge,

299
00:12:25,539 --> 00:12:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] motivacijske,

300
00:12:26,539 --> 00:12:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] kako skinuti peća skill-a.

301
00:12:28,539 --> 00:12:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Tako mi je dobre točke dao.

302
00:12:30,539 --> 00:12:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao sam, danas idim još na swaboku trener,

303
00:12:32,539 --> 00:12:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] danas još popit koji i Jackie Colu.

304
00:12:34,539 --> 00:12:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] I malo ću se na večer ovoga,

305
00:12:36,539 --> 00:12:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] najst, majoneza.

306
00:12:37,539 --> 00:12:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, rekao sam,

307
00:12:38,539 --> 00:12:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] od sutra...

308
00:12:39,539 --> 00:12:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš parizan?

309
00:12:40,539 --> 00:12:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] Rešit ćemo.

310
00:12:41,539 --> 00:12:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Neko iloška, gdje dobro.

311
00:12:43,539 --> 00:12:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sam mi daj kruha i mrt.

312
00:12:44,539 --> 00:12:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] 50 kilo si dobio.

313
00:12:46,539 --> 00:12:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dobro, to sam izgledo.

314
00:12:47,539 --> 00:12:48,539
[SPEAKER_01] I jedno sam,

315
00:12:48,539 --> 00:12:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću jedno šest puta pitati.

316
00:12:50,539 --> 00:12:53,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kur, ja ću šest puta pitati, znaš.

317
00:12:53,539 --> 00:12:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dobar, dobar.

318
00:12:54,539 --> 00:12:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] A šta ću?

319
00:12:55,539 --> 00:12:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ves stvari kako se čovjek osjeća.

320
00:12:57,539 --> 00:12:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je nemo.

321
00:12:58,539 --> 00:12:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] To smo pričali dole, ne?

322
00:12:59,539 --> 00:13:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš što, ja kad se nervoza ne volim pit,

323
00:13:00,539 --> 00:13:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] onda pojedem.

324
00:13:01,539 --> 00:13:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] A dobro, negdje ti stavno...

325
00:13:02,539 --> 00:13:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] Negdje moraš počutati.

326
00:13:03,539 --> 00:13:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš kaj ti meni ubije?

327
00:13:04,539 --> 00:13:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Meni ti noć ubije.

328
00:13:05,539 --> 00:13:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ovaj mjesec imao 17 svirki.

329
00:13:07,539 --> 00:13:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jep, sorry, je benti, pa to je super.

330
00:13:10,539 --> 00:13:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je fenomenalno.

331
00:13:11,539 --> 00:13:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jel ima ovih bendova jednomjesečno sviraju?

332
00:13:13,539 --> 00:13:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, realno, šta je tome krivo?

333
00:13:16,539 --> 00:13:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] A dobro, mi za danas imamo Jakubov posna

334
00:13:18,539 --> 00:13:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] i za one koji su možda malo poznati, nebitno šta.

335
00:13:21,539 --> 00:13:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali recimo 17 svirki, kaj ti se onda 10 dođeš doma?

336
00:13:24,539 --> 00:13:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ovoj mjesec, čekaj, sad je o 18.

337
00:13:27,539 --> 00:13:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan.

338
00:13:28,539 --> 00:13:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo reću nazad mjesec dana.

339
00:13:30,539 --> 00:13:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne šesti, da, da.

340
00:13:32,539 --> 00:13:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] Svaki drugi dan.

341
00:13:33,539 --> 00:13:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kolega, kako je turista, vodi evidenciju, ja ti to ništa vodim.

342
00:13:35,539 --> 00:13:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja pogledam kalendar, gdje smo, šta smo za vikendi.

343
00:13:37,539 --> 00:13:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ti hoću reći, onda te malo umore pili,

344
00:13:39,539 --> 00:13:41,539
[SPEAKER_00] onda te malo uzme te slatko.

345
00:13:41,539 --> 00:13:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

346
00:13:42,539 --> 00:13:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Poznat to mi sve.

347
00:13:43,539 --> 00:13:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam svirao, ali mi je poznat.

348
00:13:45,539 --> 00:13:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] Poznat to mi sve.

349
00:13:46,539 --> 00:13:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, znaš.

350
00:13:47,539 --> 00:13:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

351
00:13:48,539 --> 00:13:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] A svaka čast, dobro je dobro prosjek, svaki drugi dan, to je za danas.

352
00:13:51,539 --> 00:13:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, dobro, sam malo, iskreno, gledam smanjiti malo evo.

353
00:13:54,539 --> 00:13:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Na tri tjedna.

354
00:13:55,539 --> 00:13:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] A ti se mi slušiš tamo, na biviju?

355
00:13:56,539 --> 00:13:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] O, još se ne dam, još je dobro.

356
00:13:58,539 --> 00:13:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] Još je dobro.

357
00:13:59,539 --> 00:14:00,539
[UNKNOWN] Još je dobro.

358
00:14:00,539 --> 00:14:01,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nedamo se, bez substanci.

359
00:14:01,539 --> 00:14:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] Na fakat, evo, stvarno, taj podatak nisam znao.

360
00:14:04,539 --> 00:14:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, svatbe završavaš, privatnu festu sviraš, koncerte.

361
00:14:07,539 --> 00:14:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sviram, evo imam Marija menedžerica, ona to dogovori.

362
00:14:10,539 --> 00:14:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ono zove neko, imamo nekako ograničenje.

363
00:14:12,539 --> 00:14:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Već sam malo na privatnu festu, nije da smo, ono, ja velim, talačka kriza, rekao bi moj Marko.

364
00:14:16,539 --> 00:14:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

365
00:14:17,539 --> 00:14:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Je li talačka kriza, naš kad te ne puste doma.

366
00:14:19,539 --> 00:14:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo nekako vremesko trajanje.

367
00:14:20,539 --> 00:14:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da ih se dogovorimo, evo za ovo ljudi.

368
00:14:22,539 --> 00:14:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ti traje gaža na privatne festu? To po dogovoru ide?

369
00:14:25,539 --> 00:14:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] Po dogovoru gledamo da je uvijek dva seta po sati pol.

370
00:14:28,539 --> 00:14:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Aha. Ko koncertič neki.

371
00:14:30,539 --> 00:14:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ko koncertič, da, tako. To gledam da ona, naravno da ima mojih par frendova, a ekipe dijalno ostanemo.

372
00:14:35,539 --> 00:14:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Nije problem, mi se malo podružimo, ali znaš da pune posla, moraš malo smanjiti.

373
00:14:39,539 --> 00:14:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je onaj dan poslije ljudi koji te očekuju i žele maksimum.

374
00:14:42,539 --> 00:14:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] A jasno, a ti uvijek može biti da smijali.

375
00:14:44,539 --> 00:14:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] Promouknut strgan, mislim tak da ja sam ono malo perfekcionista na tom pogledu.

376
00:14:49,539 --> 00:14:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] I onda tako nekako se trudimo ograničiti.

377
00:14:51,539 --> 00:14:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je rekao kolega klavitorista, sada je on tih izrađenja po svadbama gdje dođemo sat vremena, rođen dana.

378
00:14:57,539 --> 00:15:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sad velimo i uvijek veli kume, veli više se vozimo, neke sviramo.

379
00:15:00,539 --> 00:15:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] A da, ali dođeš tamo.

380
00:15:02,539 --> 00:15:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] Bio ti nama i Darus Desmondo.

381
00:15:04,539 --> 00:15:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] A Darus je bio, da.

382
00:15:05,539 --> 00:15:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Isto počeo izbrigavati svadbe, čuje naporno je to.

383
00:15:08,539 --> 00:15:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je.

384
00:15:09,539 --> 00:15:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali isto tako, gost izrađenja veli sat, sat i poli.

385
00:15:12,539 --> 00:15:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, kako ne.

386
00:15:14,539 --> 00:15:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] Treš cijel noc svirat, jer.

387
00:15:15,539 --> 00:15:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa neštaj.

388
00:15:16,539 --> 00:15:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ti harmonika veli jutr nakon 12 sati sviranja?

389
00:15:18,539 --> 00:15:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa ovo.

390
00:15:19,539 --> 00:15:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] Popipaš je li vrućaj, spremiš ju.

391
00:15:21,539 --> 00:15:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa znaš šta će reći, nije ni problem svirat.

392
00:15:23,539 --> 00:15:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] Meni nikad nije bilo problem, niti jednostavno.

393
00:15:26,539 --> 00:15:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Malo mi se, malo sam ušao mogotovnje s tim dogovaranjem.

394
00:15:30,539 --> 00:15:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dogovoriš jedno, pa ti zavlja danas skroz promijene sve, pa ti šalju treće.

395
00:15:34,539 --> 00:15:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] To te više omori nek slabo svirat.

396
00:15:36,539 --> 00:15:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to nije, tak nije nekada nekada bilo.

397
00:15:38,539 --> 00:15:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja imam sve knjige od 2.4., od 2.6., znači imam sve svade koje smo cvirali ko Grupa Kispirat.

398
00:15:45,539 --> 00:15:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dan danas čuvam sve knjige.

399
00:15:47,539 --> 00:15:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš kak je to bio sastanak?

400
00:15:48,539 --> 00:15:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Novorano, Vran, Kavica, prvi ples, nije bilo kakve pjesma za ulaz, niko se nije piti.

401
00:15:53,539 --> 00:15:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi ples, i prvi ples je bilo možda 4-5 pjesma koje su se vrtili u krug.

402
00:15:57,539 --> 00:16:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] To, tortu, buket molica, super, rojitelj živi, je, hvala lijepa, odaviženje, gotovo.

403
00:16:02,539 --> 00:16:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] I tako je bilo jednostavno sve.

404
00:16:04,539 --> 00:16:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] A danas ti je stari.

405
00:16:05,539 --> 00:16:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znam po predsjedniku, on radi svadbe, fotka i to.

406
00:16:08,539 --> 00:16:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] U moje doba to je bilo jedan kamer, jedan fotkić.

407
00:16:13,539 --> 00:16:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] A kakve su bile svadbe? Niko se nije dao doma.

408
00:16:16,539 --> 00:16:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa niko dao.

409
00:16:17,539 --> 00:16:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] A sad jedva čekaju, stari dođe, darivanje.

410
00:16:19,539 --> 00:16:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ima pomoćna fotografa, pomoćna kamera, i jedan fotobut.

411
00:16:23,539 --> 00:16:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako danas, da.

412
00:16:25,539 --> 00:16:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, koliko se promijenilo.

413
00:16:27,539 --> 00:16:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to ti danas, naš, ba vani, bude koktelebar.

414
00:16:29,539 --> 00:16:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa čebi, ja ne veli da nije, to je sve lijepo.

415
00:16:31,539 --> 00:16:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

416
00:16:32,539 --> 00:16:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali se izgubila glavna čar spomeni svadbe, to su mladenci.

417
00:16:35,539 --> 00:16:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mlada se popne na stolac, ide dernek.

418
00:16:37,539 --> 00:16:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je ona.

419
00:16:38,539 --> 00:16:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ide dernek, stari, znači.

420
00:16:40,539 --> 00:16:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Niko u pet ujutro ostane 150 ljudi, niko se nema doma.

421
00:16:43,539 --> 00:16:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] I bilo napornije svirat, ali noć prošla ovako.

422
00:16:46,539 --> 00:16:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, ono je bilo veselo.

423
00:16:47,539 --> 00:16:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ču, ljudi su ove citi svega i to je tako.

424
00:16:49,539 --> 00:16:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] Je, to si dobro rekao.

425
00:16:50,539 --> 00:16:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] Citi su svega.

426
00:16:51,539 --> 00:16:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja vam prelovim, tebi predsjednik, rastave možete.

427
00:16:54,539 --> 00:16:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] Rastave, dragi gledateli, ako trebate prave fotografe.

428
00:16:59,539 --> 00:17:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] To je isto, znaš, dvije godine za svadbu i daš neku klauzun ugovor.

429
00:17:03,539 --> 00:17:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] 50% ima se na nastavu, pofusta kužiš.

430
00:17:06,539 --> 00:17:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Nije loše, da.

431
00:17:07,539 --> 00:17:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] Po to bud gratis.

432
00:17:08,539 --> 00:17:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

433
00:17:09,539 --> 00:17:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jedan po jedan.

434
00:17:10,539 --> 00:17:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan po jedan.

435
00:17:12,539 --> 00:17:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kad si toliko puno svirao, ima baš anegdote.

436
00:17:16,539 --> 00:17:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] Anegdota?

437
00:17:17,539 --> 00:17:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ima sve.

438
00:17:19,539 --> 00:17:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujem da ima, da se li samo na tebi.

439
00:17:21,539 --> 00:17:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ima sva šta je bilo.

440
00:17:23,539 --> 00:17:24,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znali smo doć, ne znam.

441
00:17:24,539 --> 00:17:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] Još smo nekad radili pratnje kad gledali svira.

442
00:17:26,539 --> 00:17:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je bilo ono, dolazimo.

443
00:17:28,539 --> 00:17:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bili mladenac, dečki u 12 kod mene doma.

444
00:17:31,539 --> 00:17:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] Naš kao, jer je rekao, sigurno tako rano, da da u 12.

445
00:17:33,539 --> 00:17:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, dođemo doma kod mladenaca.

446
00:17:35,539 --> 00:17:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] A mladenac, ip, dole živi u ono iza sedam brda.

447
00:17:40,539 --> 00:17:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sada dolazimo doma, mladenac lagano dres od repke.

448
00:17:45,539 --> 00:17:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] Slaže stolove, nema nikog.

449
00:17:47,539 --> 00:17:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sa strane ti je lagano, imaš stol, naš ono narezci.

450
00:17:51,539 --> 00:17:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš domaće kobasice.

451
00:17:52,539 --> 00:17:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] A vani u peklo, znaš kak se kobasice znoje.

452
00:17:56,539 --> 00:17:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] Komodrić na 90. minuti se kobasice znoje.

453
00:17:59,539 --> 00:18:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sa strane 2 metra gnoj, i onda lagano muhice papaju.

454
00:18:02,539 --> 00:18:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] I nema, stari, jak si glada, ne viš kada smo jeli.

455
00:18:05,539 --> 00:18:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa bilo je svega, bilo je i tuče na svadbi i svega.

456
00:18:08,539 --> 00:18:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] A to sve doživiš, to je sve normalno.

457
00:18:10,539 --> 00:18:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mora biti, ljudi ko ljudi.

458
00:18:11,539 --> 00:18:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bitno dok tebe ne gađaju kućiš.

459
00:18:12,539 --> 00:18:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dok nas ne gađaju, nisu nas nikad, hvala Boga.

460
00:18:14,539 --> 00:18:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znali smo harmoniku nekad malo zalijeti.

461
00:18:16,539 --> 00:18:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je bilo slučajno.

462
00:18:18,539 --> 00:18:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Slučajno, da.

463
00:18:19,539 --> 00:18:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] Grudnjak ništa nije doletio nikom.

464
00:18:22,539 --> 00:18:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta, je, ali ja nisam imao život prije braka, tako da nije.

465
00:18:26,539 --> 00:18:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je stvarno ovaj današnji muškar.

466
00:18:30,539 --> 00:18:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš savršeniji.

467
00:18:32,539 --> 00:18:34,539
[SPEAKER_01] Tak, po koncertima imaš šta zanimljivo.

468
00:18:34,539 --> 00:18:36,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ima, nalim ima.

469
00:18:36,539 --> 00:18:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo nekih neugodnih si ono baš.

470
00:18:38,539 --> 00:18:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mogu ne.

471
00:18:39,539 --> 00:18:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] A znaš šta, znati biti, evo ti pa sad smo svirali jedna općina.

472
00:18:42,539 --> 00:18:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pijano, bije si u vrat, dobro ne.

473
00:18:44,539 --> 00:18:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je normalno, to bi na meni problem.

474
00:18:47,539 --> 00:18:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš kada velem, imaš dobri pijanac je loši.

475
00:18:49,539 --> 00:18:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

476
00:18:50,539 --> 00:18:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je dobar pijanac imaš ono koji će, bit će dosadan, ali viš ga da je bebica.

477
00:18:53,539 --> 00:18:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

478
00:18:54,539 --> 00:18:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ma ja s tim lako, znaš, i to je duša od čovjeka i to je sve okej.

479
00:18:56,539 --> 00:18:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] Sa slušaš ga i imaju svaku svoju muku.

480
00:18:58,539 --> 00:19:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ti pa sad, bila ti jedna anegdota baš u Mariji, ne smijem viš di.

481
00:19:03,539 --> 00:19:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro.

482
00:19:04,539 --> 00:19:05,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bip, bip.

483
00:19:05,539 --> 00:19:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna općina i ljudi plate uredno sve cijena.

484
00:19:07,539 --> 00:19:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] Cijele bende je bio sa mnom, bilo vam se 8-9.

485
00:19:09,539 --> 00:19:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli orkestr mojima šonike sviramo veće za dušu.

486
00:19:11,539 --> 00:19:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] I lijevo, desno i ona tonska proba.

487
00:19:13,539 --> 00:19:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ti, naš, dignu se dva, tri ova stara pijanada.

488
00:19:16,539 --> 00:19:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bute igrali, svirali.

489
00:19:19,539 --> 00:19:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, to su neke sinice koje se tako malo dese.

490
00:19:22,539 --> 00:19:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, sad, evo, veseli se zimi, bit će puno koncerata.

491
00:19:25,539 --> 00:19:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, to je, taj koncert od dva sata je strašno intiman.

492
00:19:29,539 --> 00:19:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jer su to dvorane oko 350-500 ljudi.

493
00:19:32,539 --> 00:19:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] I, recimo, tu ti onda mi šaramo.

494
00:19:34,539 --> 00:19:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ti ne volim radit po popisu.

495
00:19:35,539 --> 00:19:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dečke sam sad od rilo, već smo se usvirali ono fino, godinu i pol.

496
00:19:39,539 --> 00:19:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ti mi sviramo od kafom i draga iz peci, do šeše načelo, do ne znam čega.

497
00:19:44,539 --> 00:19:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] Za svoju dušu.

498
00:19:45,539 --> 00:19:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] Baš za svoju dušu i to ti ljudi osjetio tvoj energiji.

499
00:19:47,539 --> 00:19:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] I to ti je, recimo, ja uvijek zamolim, ono kad dođem, rekom, nemojte mi,

500
00:19:51,539 --> 00:19:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] samo biti na mobitlu, rekom, živajte.

501
00:19:53,539 --> 00:19:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] Bogotovo naš kad je neko ovoga mlađi.

502
00:19:55,539 --> 00:19:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] A publikat je ono dosta od 5 do 95.

503
00:19:58,539 --> 00:19:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno ima ono ljudi.

504
00:19:59,539 --> 00:20:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ovdje smo god bili, to se sve proda.

505
00:20:01,539 --> 00:20:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] Svaka dvorana i baš nekako tu...

506
00:20:03,539 --> 00:20:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je, recimo, jako lijepo.

507
00:20:04,539 --> 00:20:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je, čak mi je, vjerujem, da mi je ljepše neg Lisinski.

508
00:20:07,539 --> 00:20:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] Lisinski je bilo 1910 ljudi sve skupa,

509
00:20:10,539 --> 00:20:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali intimnije je ovo.

510
00:20:12,539 --> 00:20:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

511
00:20:14,539 --> 00:20:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] Interakcija se zna malo i šalit.

512
00:20:15,539 --> 00:20:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

513
00:20:16,539 --> 00:20:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

514
00:20:17,539 --> 00:20:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

515
00:20:18,539 --> 00:20:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

516
00:20:19,539 --> 00:20:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

517
00:20:20,539 --> 00:20:21,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

518
00:20:21,539 --> 00:20:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] I nikada ja rekao, dobro sad smo sjedili, reko, hoćemo se sad malo dići.

519
00:20:23,539 --> 00:20:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] I onda presjećamo i onda ti nastane cirkus, nekakve 20 minuta svi se dignu.

520
00:20:27,539 --> 00:20:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] I baš je dobro.

521
00:20:28,539 --> 00:20:29,539
[SPEAKER_01] Super.

522
00:20:29,539 --> 00:20:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ako kad je Iron Maiden došao da vreste u Sovjetski sad.

523
00:20:31,539 --> 00:20:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] E, to, to, to, to.

524
00:20:32,539 --> 00:20:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] Vjeli pjevač, pa mi dajemo sve od sebe u i svi sjede.

525
00:20:35,539 --> 00:20:36,539
[SPEAKER_01] Svi sjede.

526
00:20:36,539 --> 00:20:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja priđem dole u publiku i on dobro, super mi je.

527
00:20:39,539 --> 00:20:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nema znaš ovo.

528
00:20:40,539 --> 00:20:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

529
00:20:41,539 --> 00:20:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kužim te, da, kužim te.

530
00:20:43,539 --> 00:20:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jel bio koji neko, najčudniji zahtjev neki za pjesmu ili nešto, ono, po željama ili.

531
00:20:49,539 --> 00:20:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa bilo ti je tipa, ne znam.

532
00:20:51,539 --> 00:20:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ima ti ono, svadba bila jedna, to se sjećam kad je.

533
00:20:54,539 --> 00:20:56,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi ti rekao, aj može nešto od Brkova.

534
00:20:56,539 --> 00:20:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] Od Brkova, da, da, da.

535
00:20:57,539 --> 00:20:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] Četala meni sveće.

536
00:20:58,539 --> 00:20:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, to bi znali, da.

537
