1303
00:43:41,539 --> 00:43:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tijeli nekakvu tu komunikaciju, je to je prirodno došlo?

1304
00:43:43,539 --> 00:43:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] Odličan potis.

1305
00:43:44,539 --> 00:43:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1306
00:43:45,539 --> 00:43:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] Odličan potis.

1307
00:43:46,539 --> 00:43:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to je prirodno došlo, nije ništa ciljano.

1308
00:43:48,539 --> 00:43:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi, ti ljuda joj probudiš pjesmami.

1309
00:43:50,539 --> 00:43:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nekakve slikice uvijek gledam lepe u baci tu jutro, ali ti si...

1310
00:43:54,539 --> 00:43:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko već to traje?

1311
00:43:55,539 --> 00:43:56,539
[SPEAKER_01] Sam znam da mi izletiš.

1312
00:43:56,539 --> 00:43:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, ja znaš od korone srti, ja krenuo kad sam imao vremena.

1313
00:43:58,539 --> 00:44:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] Odmah, sad mi je počelo iskakat.

1314
00:44:00,539 --> 00:44:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] Eto vi godine došlo do mene.

1315
00:44:02,539 --> 00:44:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] Gle, Gorica, Karlova...

1316
00:44:03,539 --> 00:44:05,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ba da, baš je daleko.

1317
00:44:05,539 --> 00:44:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dok to do leti, kužiš.

1318
00:44:06,539 --> 00:44:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] Baš je daleko.

1319
00:44:07,539 --> 00:44:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali pazi, za dobro jutro...

1320
00:44:08,539 --> 00:44:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] Je, je, je, je.

1321
00:44:09,539 --> 00:44:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi još recimo nešto bitnije možda za kraj.

1322
00:44:12,539 --> 00:44:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam to sad, puno stvari nisam znao.

1323
00:44:14,539 --> 00:44:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ti i tvoja supraga...

1324
00:44:16,539 --> 00:44:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] Prava Božja išta, Fičo, svaka čak.

1325
00:44:18,539 --> 00:44:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ti i tvoja supraga, mladi ljudi, zapusleni.

1326
00:44:21,539 --> 00:44:23,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto, dajte savjet, imam biti.

1327
00:44:23,539 --> 00:44:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] Može se, radite puno, radiš puno.

1328
00:44:25,539 --> 00:44:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] Radimo puno, da li smo dosta iskukla?

1329
00:44:26,539 --> 00:44:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali eto, imate i djeta, imate i sve.

1330
00:44:28,539 --> 00:44:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Je, imamo dva dječa.

1331
00:44:30,539 --> 00:44:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ništa, savjet ostati u Hrvatskoj.

1332
00:44:33,539 --> 00:44:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] I ako treba raditi dva posla sam da smo sve tu na Hrpi.

1333
00:44:36,539 --> 00:44:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo prekrasnu zemlju koju trebamo čubati i uživati.

1334
00:44:42,539 --> 00:44:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ma nećak se, imam sada posla.

1335
00:44:44,539 --> 00:44:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek se neko pojavi, neko bi pomogal.

1336
00:44:46,539 --> 00:44:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad ti vidim ove nepalčeke i ove jadne kevele z ovih crnim amodom.

1337
00:44:50,539 --> 00:44:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Meni žal ti ljudi.

1338
00:44:52,539 --> 00:44:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] To su ljudi koji se isti otiče trbom za kruhom.

1339
00:44:54,539 --> 00:44:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ima posla za sve.

1340
00:44:56,539 --> 00:44:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] Treba delati, treba živjeti.

1341
00:44:58,539 --> 00:45:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] Treba povesti dobar komad mesa, popit koju čašicu vina.

1342
00:45:00,539 --> 00:45:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] Malo Hanjekena.

1343
00:45:02,539 --> 00:45:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Nećemo reklamirati.

1344
00:45:04,539 --> 00:45:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pustit ćemo im to.

1345
00:45:06,539 --> 00:45:08,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nama je svejedno njima mu menat za cijeli život.

1346
00:45:08,539 --> 00:45:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, to je to.

1347
00:45:10,539 --> 00:45:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš kaj ti vidiš, tri pod sedam.

1348
00:45:12,539 --> 00:45:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, uvića sam imao 21, danas je već 36.

1349
00:45:14,539 --> 00:45:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, treba i uživati, treba radi.

1350
00:45:16,539 --> 00:45:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] Treba sve naći nekakvu sredinu koliko se da naći.

1351
00:45:18,539 --> 00:45:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

1352
00:45:20,539 --> 00:45:22,539
[SPEAKER_00] Siniša, svaka čast. Hvala ti puno.

1353
00:45:22,539 --> 00:45:24,539
[SPEAKER_01] Evo tebi ruka. Hvala ti.

1354
00:45:24,539 --> 00:45:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ekipa, zapratite Sinišu, a i nas tu i tamo nešto.

1355
00:45:26,539 --> 00:45:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] I za više recepta.

1356
00:45:28,539 --> 00:45:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] Obratite se predsjedniku.

1357
00:45:30,539 --> 00:45:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] Predsjedniku našemu, tako je.

1358
00:45:32,539 --> 00:45:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] Veliki pozdrav.

